{"tid":101262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄摩爾曼斯克兩支那遊客為自拍而橫穿馬路遭車撞","createTime":"2017-01-30T16:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T03:27:16.000Z","uid":37661,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b34407905bd39f946ba70aa6f3306da87ac4fde9","tid":101262,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:20:45.000Z","msg":"俄摩爾曼斯克兩支那遊客為自拍而橫穿馬路遭車撞 一死一傷<br />\n<br />\n北京新浪網 01-26 19:57<br />\n<br />\n【環球網報導 記者 李德意】俄羅斯衛星網1月26日援引Nord-News網站報導稱，2名支那遊客在摩爾曼斯克州因自拍而違規橫穿馬路被車撞。事故造成一名女子身亡，另一名男子多處骨折。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，上述兩人為與摩爾曼斯克景點標誌塔自拍合影而違規橫穿馬路。該標誌塔是摩爾曼斯克市的標誌性景點，其底部圓環上標註著該市經緯度，塔頂則立有一艘帆船。<br />\n<br />\n摩爾曼斯克州內務局新聞處主任稱：「車禍於25日晚上發生在標誌塔附近，支那遊客在該景點前自拍，兩人為了離標誌塔近些決定違規橫穿公路，結果被一輛富豪XC 90撞到。」<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，救護車將兩人送往當地醫院。女子夜間因傷重不治身亡，男子有多處骨折。當地警方稱，司機並未酒後駕駛，目前正在對事故進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n男傷者家人在網上求助<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/v53obj2m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fv53obj2m&h=d53728f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報導截圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.news.sina.com.tw/article/images/news-14854329015074.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.news.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-14854329015074.jpg&h=86bc78b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20170126/20416308.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.news.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20170126%2F20416308.html&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=d752d54f\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20170126/20416308.html</a>"},{"pid":"05506f7c1ee302766fd5aa7ae1396f31708a598f","tid":101262,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2852f34c88cf4c22100fa9f04dd637d610a8a90d","tid":101262,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:30:07.000Z","msg":"又死1隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92b1e282481fb236d751a939aab626f9bef82b1","tid":101262,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:32:27.000Z","msg":"俄人：唔驚 普京照我哋"},{"pid":"0259c715f9a8e099e3730525869ec90021414283","tid":101262,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T16:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又死1隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你做唔到嘢呀～<br />\n<br />\n咁都搵唔到呢段新聞。"},{"pid":"d4b9fade1b4701066c3a3c8c2fe53bd4921c98b0","tid":101262,"uid":12232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:09:47.000Z","msg":"犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8dad0485ace93de052f1a82ea2f07b120f4180c","tid":101262,"uid":57700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:11:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88d5651d0c9a5e2460f567e8348409671fb954c0","tid":101262,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:12:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又死1隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你做唔到嘢呀～<br />\n<br />\n咁都搵唔到呢段新聞。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打辛苦晒<br />\n<a href=\"http://呢幾日na.cx\" data-sr-url=\"http